    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts crisp engagement from its individual throttle bodies and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement check. The chassis maintains excellent torsional rigidity, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. A well-sorted driver's car that delivers authentic M-division feedback.",
